text: Ramush Haradinaj (born 3 July 1968) is a Kosovar politician. He was leader of the AAK party, and was the 3rd Prime Minister of Kosovo. He is a former officer and leader of the Kosovo Liberation Army (KLA), and previously served as Prime Minister of Kosovo between 2004 and 2005. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Kosovo Category:Kosovo Albanians
title: Ramush Haradinaj
